data.description: This beautiful and spacious master cape cod has four bedrooms and two full baths.  Upon entering the home the feel of an open concept with the living room with hardwood floors and a fireplace,  full dining room and lovely bright first floor family room with sliding patio doors.  The eat in kitchen is large with ceramic flooring.  Two ample size bedrooms on the first floor.  Upstairs you will find an additional bedroom and a very large master bedroom and bath.  Great recreation room for family and sports entertainment. Your major maintenance has definitely been taken care of,  hot water tank and dishwasher (2024), furnace and vinyl windows(2017)Newer carpet in the basement (2020) Patio doors (2024).  This one is 2100 square feet, don't let the outside fool you!  Come tour and make this beauty your own!
